## 10 Mandatory Business Rules ‚Üí Implementation Map

| # | Rule | Where Enforced | How |
|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | Registration number unique | `transit.vehicle` | `_sql_constraints` + inline Python error |
| 2 | Retired/In Shop hidden from dispatch | Trip form | `vehicle_id` domain `[('status','=','available')]` |
| 3 | Expired/Suspended driver blocked | Trip form + `action_dispatch()` | Driver domain filter + Python validation |
| 4 | On Trip = can't double-assign | Trip form | Domain `status='available'` covers this |
| 5 | Cargo ‚â§ capacity | `@api.constrains` + `action_dispatch()` | `ValidationError` with capacity details |
| 6 | Dispatch ‚Üí both On Trip | `action_dispatch()` | Sets `vehicle.status` + `driver.status` = `on_trip` |
| 7 | Complete ‚Üí both Available | `action_complete()` | Resets both + updates odometer + creates fuel log |
| 8 | Cancel ‚Üí both Available | `action_cancel()` | Resets both (only if was dispatched) |
| 9 | Active maintenance ‚Üí In Shop | `create()` override | Sets `vehicle.status = 'in_shop'` |
| 10 | Close maintenance ‚Üí Available | `action_close()` | Checks retired status first |

